data-triple-N3.o: "The University of Utah (also referred to as The U, the U of U or Utah) is a public coeducational space-grant research university in Salt Lake City, Utah, United States. As the state's flagship university, Utah offers more than 100 undergraduate majors and more than 90 graduate degree programs. Graduate studies include the S.J. Quinney College of Law and the School of Medicine, Utah's only medical school."@en
